Example Quantitative PCR data

A dataset containing Bio-Rad qPCR data for IFNbeta and Actin upon transfection with RNA ligands.

qpcr

Format

A tibble containing 145 observations of 6 variables.

well

plate well

fluor

Fluorophore

target

mRNA target

content

well containing reference standard

sample

sample name

cq

Quantification cycle

Source

Rachel Ancar

Examples

qpcr
#> # A tibble: 145 x 6
#>     well fluor  target content       sample       cq
#>    <chr> <chr>   <chr>   <chr>        <chr>    <dbl>

#>  3   A03  SYBR IFNbeta Unkn-03         5ppp 18.45676

#>  7   A07  SYBR IFNbeta Unkn-07          3p2 19.10928
